items.sentence: Tom didn't get a chance to say goodbye to Mary.
Tom didn't expect to be asked to give a speech.
Tom could hear people talking in the next room.
Tom came to church last week with his children.
Tom came out of his house and got into his car.
Tom called Mary at 2:30, but she didn't answer.
Tom got angry when he saw Mary talking to John.
Tom goes to Boston whenever he has a chance to.
Tom doesn't know how he's going to do that yet.
Tom didn't want to tell Mary what had happened.
